body_text.text:
Final follow-up was on April 10, 2020. In the ITT population, the time to clinical improvement in the remdesivir group was not significantly different to that of the control group (median 21·0 days [IQR 13·0–28·0] in the remdesivir group vs 23·0 days [15·0–28·0]; HR 1·23 [95% CI 0·87–1·75]; table 3
, figure 2
).
